txt.en: Seek out Lithgor Sandwolf and tell him of your accomplishments.

'[placeholder], many here have now heard the tale of your struggles against the dark forces that stir in Angmar. Perhaps not all can be trusted, but I am sure that there are many among my people who would aid you, if they can. While I fear that greater horrors than either of us can imagine await you, I have faith in your strength and perserverence. Fare thee well, [placeholder]'.'
